Author: bumbumboleji
Text: Don’t worry we have all done some version of this at some point. Yeah just don’t say anything but if he brings it up admit it casually like “yeah, I got hungry” and depending on how you sort things out maybe ask if he wants you to replace the items? You know your relationship better than us, but don’t sweat it, he probably won’t even notice.

Text: Honestly just act normal and dont bring attention to it. Hopefully he wont even.m notice.
